&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;&lt;!-- DIV {margin:0px;} --&gt;&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-family:times new roman, new york, times, serif;font-size:12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-family: times new roman,new york,times,serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;&quot;Have none of you&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;&quot;&gt; never wondered why some files here are amazingly clear while others&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;&quot;&gt; are far closer to what actually happens with any of the devices? Has&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;&quot;&gt; no one else questioned this, even to yourself?&quot;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;No, I do not question them or their reality. No one is born spiritually equal! We all have different levels of experience, psi abilities and connections. For me to say that everyone should get the same connection as me would be unfair and naive. I would expect that there are
 many people who get better and worse. I am grateful that I can get a connection at all. This unfounded jealousy is exactly what brought down INIT.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;
Do you accept everything you see and hear from everyone at face value?&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;Yes, I do! Who am I to question yours or anyone else&#39;s reality? What you believe is true, is true in your world.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;
Do you never have ideas on how things might be improved? Do you never question? &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;Sure, I have several experimental pieces of equipment that have given me different degrees of success in the clarity of communication. The equipment is only a small part though. Your attitude and intentions are what will strengthen or weaken your transdimensional bonds. If you are having a bad day or harbor feelings of resentment, jealousy or hate your chances of connecting with something higher than the earth plane are slim. Not many beings want to come down to this dark level unless they are already here. Usually, these beings are identified by their pleas for help or a streak of nastiness. The higher beings that are around them are usually gatekeepers and &quot;social workers&quot; as I call them. The social workers are the ones trying to help the earthbound spirits to move up and out of the darkness. Gatekeepers facilitate your communication channels.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Anyways,
 you get the gist.... Bottom line is, if experimenters want to improve transcommunication then they have to work on themselves and not their equipment.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;PS: See there is no reason to use nastiness to respond to questions. Being confident in what you know allows for a calm response.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Regards,&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Frank R.&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;border-left: 2px solid rgb(16, 16, 255); margin: 5px 0px 5px 5px; padding-left: 5px; font-family: times new roman,new york,times,serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;----- Original Message ----&lt;br&gt;From: babiarz3 &lt;babiarz3@...&gt;&lt;br&gt;To: EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com&lt;br&gt;Sent: Monday, January 21, 2008 6:45:02 PM&lt;br&gt;Subject: [EVP-ITC] Re: Babs has Issues!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;








