            &lt;p&gt;I never said Frank was misguided or selfish but, I&#39;m not surprised you&lt;br&gt;
construed it that way.&lt;br&gt;
Research and researchers in the truest form of the word is and are&lt;br&gt;
open to critique and suggestions. So, no, in the truest meaning I&lt;br&gt;
don&#39;t believe so. My comments were absolutely valid and could have&lt;br&gt;
been used in a productive manner but, instead I was deflected and&lt;br&gt;
