For myself, I believe it is of utmost importance to have an accurate&lt;br&gt;
view of what is really happening. Edited files may indeed be very&lt;br&gt;
accurate but there is no way to tell when the raw is not available and&lt;br&gt;
it causes me great concern that the suggestion was met with such&lt;br&gt;
