with recording and developing devices to do so. That&#39;s fine. Recording&lt;br&gt;
the communications is a good thing. But my opinions thoughts, etc are&lt;br&gt;
not welcome here or desired. That&#39;s fine too. &lt;br&gt;
I wish you all the best in your en devours. Sincerely.&lt;br&gt;
